00:00:23.070 --> 00:00:27.100
NEEMA NASSIR: So good
afternoon, everyone.

00:00:27.100 --> 00:00:30.060
Today, we are going to continue
the discussion regarding

00:00:30.060 --> 00:00:34.570
short-range planning
for transit agencies.

00:00:34.570 --> 00:00:39.870
And if you do not have
the set of slides,

00:00:39.870 --> 00:00:43.710
the handout from last week,
there are extra copies here.

