paths that they choose,

00:56:49.080 --> 00:56:52.510
given their available
path alternatives,

00:56:52.510 --> 00:57:00.150
and you can basically calibrate
these coefficients based

00:57:00.150 --> 00:57:02.160
on the assumption
that passengers

00:57:02.160 --> 00:57:05.730
try to maximize their
utility or minimize

00:57:05.730 --> 00:57:08.355
