01:06:28.617 --> 01:06:29.450
That's a good point.

01:06:29.450 --> 01:06:33.320
So probably the
important caveats

01:06:33.320 --> 01:06:35.960
is that many of these
guidelines and standards

01:06:35.960 --> 01:06:38.540
are not from the
