01:06:38.540 --> 01:06:42.680
So passenger's perspective
performance measures

01:06:42.680 --> 01:06:47.080
and passenger's
perspective perceptions

01:06:47.080 --> 01:06:49.190
of the quality of
service is something

01:06:49.190 --> 01:06:51.377
that probably should
be incorporated

01:06:51.377 --> 01:06:52.460
in some of these measures.

