01:08:04.190 --> 01:08:08.180
That's something that could
be identified thinking of it

01:08:08.180 --> 01:08:14.120
as an optimization problem as
an optimal or objective function

01:08:14.120 --> 01:08:17.649
to be optimized over the
solution of space, which

01:08:17.649 --> 01:08:19.460
is the guidelines,
existing guidelines

01:08:19.460 --> 01:08:22.460
and standards in the service.

01:08:22.460 --> 01:08:26.840
So what this guideline
