01:08:26.840 --> 01:08:30.890
here is just the bound
on what is acceptable

01:08:30.890 --> 01:08:32.700
and what's not acceptable.

01:08:32.700 --> 01:08:36.649
But the fact that is this going
to be beneficial to the system

01:08:36.649 --> 01:08:37.640
or not?

