But the marginal
rate of substitutions

01:12:05.470 --> 01:12:10.560
of these coefficients related
to different components,

01:12:10.560 --> 01:12:12.390
that's something that
can be quantified.

01:12:12.390 --> 01:12:15.720
For example, what
is the disutility

01:12:15.720 --> 01:12:19.740
of waiting time as
compared to the disutility

01:12:19.740 --> 01:12:20.970
of in-vehicle time.

01:12:20.970 --> 01:12:27.228
So that's a way kind of have a
sense of the generalized cost.

